Here's a Christmas card message that emphasizes teamwork while appreciating your colleague's abilities and contributions:


---

Dear [Colleague's Name],

Merry Christmas and Happy New Year! I just wanted to take a moment to express my gratitude for your incredible work and collaboration this year. Your skills and expertise have been invaluable to the success of our projects. It’s been a true pleasure working together, and I’m proud of what we’ve achieved as a team.

Looking forward to continuing our great partnership and reaching even more goals in the future!

Best regards,
[Your Name]


---

This message highlights the success of the team effort while still appreciating the colleague's abilities and cooperation.

